pulong ng management team sa isang oras.

893
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:17,160
Bakit ka nakatingin sakin?

894
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:19,320
Sinabi sa iyo ni Mr. Ji na ipaalam sa kanila, kaya pumunta ka.

895
00:40:20,590 --> 00:40:21,710
Okay, Mr. Ji.

896
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:28,350
Salamat sa iyong suporta, Mr. Wei.

897
00:40:28,220 --> 00:40:30,250
[Opisina ng General Manager]

898
00:40:28,550 --> 00:40:29,990
Syempre.

899
00:40:30,660 --> 00:40:32,950
Gusto mo bang ipakita ko sayo?

900
00:40:36,110 --> 00:40:36,630
Hindi na kailangan.

901
00:40:37,070 --> 00:40:38,790
Magpapalit na ako.

902
00:40:38,830 --> 00:40:39,630
Magkita tayo mamaya

903
00:40:39,660 --> 00:40:40,790
